message.entry: 掩膜的世界坐标系范围(XWorldLimits 和 YWorldLimits)应与对应的 bigimage 在指定级别上的范围相同。
The countEachLabel method is supported only for categorical images. Not all input images are categorical.
Categorical bigimages must all have the same categories specified in the Classes property.
UseParallel 需要 Parallel Computing Toolbox 和并行池。
